uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model

Class DFieldViewer<V,F extends DField<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.DFieldViewer<V,F>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DFieldView<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DArrayViewer, DCellViewer

    public class DFieldViewer<V,F extends DField<V>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DFieldView<V>
    Represents a view of a field in the Object Model (OM). Provides methods for accessing the current state of the field, but not for editing it.
